<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .contact-info p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .home-link {
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #5a6268;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .home-link:hover {
            background-color: #444d55;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <div class="container">
    
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our bank! We are dedicated to providing excellent financial services to our customers.</p>
        <p>Our bank has been serving the community for over 50 years, and we pride ourselves on our commitment to integrity, reliability, and customer satisfaction.</p>
        <p>For any inquiries, feel free to contact us:</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Main Street, Cityville, State, Country</p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@bank.com</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary home-link">Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
